@startuml state-login
title freepeepee : login UI states

[*] --> Closed : route /login

state Closed
state Opening
state Revealing
state Open
state Submitting
state Failed
state Authenticated

Closed --> Opening      : click door
Opening --> Revealing   : after 950 ms\n(door fully swung)
Revealing --> Open      : after 750 ms\n(newspaper rises)

Open --> Submitting     : submit() with valid form
Submitting --> Authenticated : 200 OK\n(navigate /list)
Submitting --> Failed        : 401 / network error
Failed --> Open              : after 600 ms (paper shake stops)

Authenticated --> [*]
@enduml
